{"tid":1873878,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎係人工病毒","createTime":"2020-02-11T01:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T02:34:26.000Z","uid":33263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"080c1f5b60ea64f6515f9697e2ae317440b2df4f","tid":1873878,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"以性命担保研究病毒未泄露的石正丽，2015年发表的论文<br />\n2015年，著名的自然医学电子刊物上发表了一篇论文，主要作者为中国科学院武汉病毒学研究所、武汉大学病毒研究所教授石正丽。<br />\n这篇论文说，他们医学研究发现，只要把蝙蝠身上的S蛋白里的ACE2这个受体开关一调，这个病毒马上就可以传染给人类。利用病毒基因重组技术将蝙蝠的S蛋白和小老鼠的Sars病毒重组，得到的新病毒可以和人体的血管紧张素转化酶2（ACE2）结合，能很有效地感染人类的呼吸道细胞，毒性巨大。他们发现新病毒明显地损害了老鼠的肺部，所有疫苗管失去作用。于是，石正丽团队继续用猴子做实验，模拟病毒在人体上的效果。<br />\n这个实验当时引起美国医学界非常大的争议，医学专家Declan Butler也在Nature Medicine上撰文表示，这种实验没有什么意义，而且风险很大。由于缺乏技术，当时石正丽团队是和美国北卡罗莱纳的一个医学小组合作。2014年美国疾病控制中心意识到这个病毒有可能成为生物化学武器时，立刻已经叫停了这种病毒改造计划，并停止拨款给相关的研究。<br />\n<br />\n这是Declan Butler 质疑文章 （写于2015年）的链接。 <a href=\"https://www.nature.com/news/engineered-bat-virus-stirs-debate-over-risky-research-1.18787?fbclid=IwAR3DUjcRIlGF5_d6XOS4mm_ZlzWUwgGaHZZPYVp3_UaznsQWsftDU5EVQDY#/ref-link-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Fnews%2Fengineered-bat-virus-stirs-debate-over-risky-research-1.18787%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3DUjcRIlGF5_d6XOS4mm_ZlzWUwgGaHZZPYVp3_UaznsQWsftDU5EVQDY%23%2Fref-link-2&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4QXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=4f48d6f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/news/engineered-bat-virus-stirs-debate-over-risky-research-1.18787?fbclid=IwAR3DUjcRIlGF5_d6XOS4mm_ZlzWUwgGaHZZPYVp3_UaznsQWsftDU5EVQDY#/ref-link-2</a><br />\n以下是石正丽及团队发表的关于改造蝙幅沙士病毒研究文章的链接。（写于2015年） <a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/nm.3985?fbclid=IwAR0iTTfDlT-uxNFPtvQH-xFrF6QaF1hKE1Ey2TPrEi17XfFUElbpUlAosDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fnm.3985%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0iTTfDlT-uxNFPtvQH-xFrF6QaF1hKE1Ey2TPrEi17XfFUElbpUlAosDc&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4QXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=fe6214e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/nm.3985?fbclid=IwAR0iTTfDlT-uxNFPtvQH-xFrF6QaF1hKE1Ey2TPrEi17XfFUElbpUlAosDc</a><br />\n以下是论文简介的一句话及翻译<br />\nUsing the SARS-CoV reverse genetics system2, we generated and characterized a chimeric virus expressing the spike of bat coronavirus SHC014 in a mouse-adapted SARS-CoV backbone.<br />\n谷歌直译为：使用SARS-CoV反向遗传学系统2，我们生成并鉴定了一种在适应小鼠的SARS-CoV主干中表达蝙蝠冠状病毒SHC014的尖峰的嵌合病毒。"},{"pid":"b47d3e7ad477b0bc097940b616da978a1534daff","tid":1873878,"uid":18251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"中國人製造2019"},{"pid":"d2273c698be806696d13a3a1ad80fd498292b8e5","tid":1873878,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"中共刻意投毒 希望香港止暴制亂"},{"pid":"88825c18b725d862f52820f861f085c7d17d3a54","tid":1873878,"uid":195821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"好文一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c2036760b06e8eed0c07547e722f53f92e0990","tid":1873878,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:16:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dff144b6f8b052aed0a7edbac53320e61d53a53f","tid":1873878,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5281968f80fb348e958fd23fa44f152d7d8f8563","tid":1873878,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff144b6f8b052aed0a7edbac53320e61d53a53f","tid":1873878,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}